  `element_textarea` text COMMENT 'The textarea element represents a multiline plain text edit control for the element''s raw value. The contents of the control represent the control''s default value.',
  `element_keygen` text COMMENT 'The keygen element represents a key pair generator control. When the control''s form is submitted, the private key is stored in the local keystore, and the public key is packaged and sent to the server.',
  `element_output` text COMMENT 'The output element represents the result of a calculation.',
  `element_progress` text COMMENT 'The progress element represents the completion progress of a task. The progress is either indeterminate, indicating that progress is being made but that it is not clear how much more work remains to be done before the task is complete (e.g. because the ta',
  `element_meter` text COMMENT 'The meter element represents a scalar measurement within a known range, or a fractional value; for example disk usage, the relevance of a query result, or the fraction of a voting population to have selected a particular candidate.',
  `element_input_attribute_type_value_hidden` text COMMENT 'The input element represents a value that is not intended to be examined or manipulated by the user.',
  `element_input_attribute_type_value_text` text COMMENT 'The input element represents a one line plain text edit control for the element''s value.',
  `element_input_attribute_type_value_search` text COMMENT 'The input element represents a one line plain text edit control for the element''s value.',
